query:
SELECT
                al.user_id as "user_id!",
                u.email as user_email,
                COUNT(*)::bigint as "count!"
            FROM audit_logs al
            LEFT JOIN users u ON al.user_id = u.id
            WHERE al.user_id IS NOT NULL
              AND al.created_at >= $1::date
            GROUP BY al.user_id, u.email
            ORDER BY 3 DESC
            LIMIT 10
